data.title: Excavating Contractors Michigan
data.meta_description: Mid Michigan Excavating Company specializing in commercial and residential projects such as sewer lines, water lines, ponds, lakes, land clearing, drain fields, drive ways, gradeing and much more
data.text: Allow us to provide a detailed Free Estimate on your next project. Our state-of-art estimating and earth quantity software will take away any Surprises. Our experienced and knowledgeable crews will expedite your project in a safe and competitive manner. Our laser-guided machinery ensure that projects are on-grade and on-time.
